[Our thanks to Ramon for sharing this document with us.

Making vaccination compulsory and achieving 100 percent participation are 2 separate states, as we all know. But the incidence is decreasing, and with success will come better rancher confidence and involvement. They will succeed and probably within the next 10 years.

Maps of Argentina can be found at http://www.lib.utexas.edu/maps/americas/argentina_pol96.jpg and http://healthmap.org/r/1yJb. A map of Buenos Aires province can be found at https://maps.google.com/maps?q=map+buenos+aires+province. - Mod.MHJ]
